{"tid":146251,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"高松四日三夜玩左八百幾公里痴左線遊記（自駕）","createTime":"2017-03-07T02:37:37.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-09T15:51:13.000Z","uid":33988,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"5a5e97d56c07c96dad4251e8c80dd7f1514ca62d","tid":146251,"uid":33988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:37:37.000Z","msg":"第一次打遊記，因為今次旅行實在太激太難忘，晚晚玩到天光咁滯所以想記念下分享下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n《事前準備》<br />\n<br />\n因為同3個fd去只夾得四日假而快運咁啱高松有平又啱時間所以就揀左高松，雖然唔知有咩玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n買完之後發現原來高松同四國係以風景同慢活為主，啲野又早收，就諗住不如揸車去遠啲，去埋神戶同大阪，反正4個人入去有3個都揸得，就造就了今次瘋狂之旅。<br />\n<br />\n經過一番搜尋協商之後，最後得出以下行程<br />\n<br />\nDay 1: 落機-拎車-金刀比羅宮-德島youme mall-德島麵王-住淡路島bnb<br />\n<br />\nDay 2: 鳴門漩渦-神戶鐵人廿八公園-睇神戶勝利船-大阪食宵夜-淡路島bnb<br />\n<br />\nDay 3: 祖谷蔓橋-小便小僧-大步危峽-高松機場酒店check in-高松市區-高松機場酒店<br />\n<br />\nDay 4: 食烏冬-還車-番香港"},{"pid":"72b9072c76e4f16463f360b413e440ac51af6ab4","tid":146251,"uid":33988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T03:16:39.000Z","msg":"《第一日》<br />\n搭9點機，7點搭機場快線，在香港站順手check in。4個人搭有優惠每人70蚊<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0r8jc9i.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0r8jc9i.jpg&h=f378c58f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nDelay左大半個鐘，去到高松機場已經兩點鐘喇，跟手就去拎車出發去金刀比羅宮，俾日本人形容為一生人要去一次的神舍<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6v0M85a.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6v0M85a.jpg&h=168d9d1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n今次靠晒呢架vitz<br />\n<br />\n四點左右去到金刀比羅山下停車場，沿路有條表參道，兩邊有好多唔同嘅鋪頭，行完表參道之後就要上山喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/105742_c213b657ebc91e43155c20bc5cbecdae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F105742_c213b657ebc91e43155c20bc5cbecdae.jpg&h=8a18f44d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n又凍又餓整串燒丸子真係不得了<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/110119_f40ea745b9378187f3b9e3253bec909e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F110119_f40ea745b9378187f3b9e3253bec909e.jpg&h=4dd06e19&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n呢張表參道相上網搵的因為無影到<br />\n<br />\n由停車場去到本宮有700幾級，雖然沿路都有其他嘢睇但700幾級真係好累<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/110611_ff059db616ebba58b9ac0d4820d206eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F110611_ff059db616ebba58b9ac0d4820d206eb.jpg&h=f13b56a2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n回頭望下都好靚，包括日本妹<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/M7057Vy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FM7057Vy.jpg&h=ac9b2259&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n唔知係咪叫你笑住行無咁辛苦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/9u19tPJ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F9u19tPJ.jpg&h=1ee375f8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n金刀比羅狗 相傳係話以前日本人怕辛苦會派隻狗幫手<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/111245_77758ded549a03811621802ac9b130cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F111245_77758ded549a03811621802ac9b130cb.jpg&h=9235e9fa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8x8Fh1X.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8x8Fh1X.jpg&h=7ca7aa83&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/111246_77758ded549a03811621802ac9b130cb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F111246_77758ded549a03811621802ac9b130cb.jpg&h=717c5e58&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n上到去 個景仲靚過個宮 香港唔知幾耐無見過<br />\n真係好靚，上到去睇左陣行左陣買埋御守就落山喇"},{"pid":"0cdfa62983fc463457a4f199c08fddfb082858be","tid":146251,"uid":55232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T04:58:10.000Z","msg":"LM<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"99b302124ac2f71f486b757a7df95c2ad58ee193","tid":146251,"uid":8203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:08:44.000Z","msg":"高松市區有咩景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nday3住祖谷個邊既溫泉旅館就正"},{"pid":"b67bd9e5108263c4abdb48aaddaac0b37534830c","tid":146251,"uid":33988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T06:29:57.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>高松市區有咩景點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nday3住祖谷個邊既溫泉旅館就正</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n本身有諗過但第四日要十二點半還車  祖谷揸番過去都兩個鐘  以我地起唔到身嘅性格一定趕唔切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n所以突登揀左間近機場同還車嘅酒店以防萬一<br />\n<br />\n至於高松有咩玩就可以繼續睇埋落去呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7b66674f9575c39bd251e3468263f12d1713c3df","tid":146251,"uid":33988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T07:07:31.000Z","msg":"《繼續第一日》<br />\n<br />\n落山之後都5點幾 自從香港機場7點幾食左個水手早餐之後就係上出前果幾串小丸子 已經餓到仆街 拿拿臨出發去綾川食迴轉壽司 貪佢又順路又平 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AwatbC7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAwatbC7.jpg&h=0e86687e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n我每次去日本都會搵呢間食 又平又好味停車場又大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/143612_486ec6b354cc497cfd35336e89d714ae.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F143612_486ec6b354cc497cfd35336e89d714ae.jpg&h=27039b59&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HoV8vF2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHoV8vF2.jpg&h=de05dc93&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/143613_b62eef37afa355fce26274c5476643a0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F143613_b62eef37afa355fce26274c5476643a0.jpg&h=969f3bf6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n普通好似係90-100yen一碟兩件 貴價野就一件咁<br />\n港紙8蚊食到一件長腳蟹/海膽/蟹膏 抵撚到不得了<br />\n<br />\n食7咁食之後出發去德島市 德島市最出名係拉麵 眉山同阿波舞 但由於我地入到去都天黑同埋對阿波舞都冇咩興趣 所以我地淨係安排左行街同食拉麵<br />\n<br />\n德島市入面d鋪頭其實都好早收 但上網見到市區出少少叫藍住町嘅地方有間you me mall 開到十點 又有好大個停車場 所以就去左喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/144734_312a7a80ca081cc7422dae33fe9d81cd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F144734_312a7a80ca081cc7422dae33fe9d81cd.jpg&h=98879e01&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n都係上網搵圖冇影相<br />\n<br />\n揸左個零中左右就去到 入面都有好多野行 uniqulo/ global work / muji/ abc mart/ namco/ supersports xebio咁/ 仲有間超市同百貨 我會覺得佢似荃灣廣場咁嘅氣氛但大好多<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/145407_1460d431ce220da61af4300fb5827bc8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F145407_1460d431ce220da61af4300fb5827bc8.jpg&h=dd1764c2&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/V1zk3Tj.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FV1zk3Tj.jpg&h=0041ed82&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n行到人地收鋪就揸去市中心食麵王 麵王收12點我地11點3去到 門口買食劵入去搵位坐好快就有得食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e6d8y7z.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe6d8y7z.jpg&h=3e3d1451&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/145640_6fee389e92618f88ff7ebe46b366b4e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F145640_6fee389e92618f88ff7ebe46b366b4e0.jpg&h=7f7ea31f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n最出名嘅窩蛋豬肉飯同拉麵<br />\n拉麵個湯較濃但份量同配料都好多同好好食<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n佢仲有個餃子都好出色 但第二晚食完大阪王將就覺得天外有天<br />\n<br />\n飲飽食醉之後番淡路島bnb 沿途去全家補給下買下生果嘢飲搞搞下去到bnb都成2點 好在呢間係整套房子亦同屋主單左聲話會夜 佢覆番我幾點check in只要靜點就得喇 時間呢個都係我地嘅旅程好緊要嘅一個原素 <br />\n<br />\n入到屋搞個熱水爐好耐都唔識搞 每次熱水都係好快就冇 每人平均匆匆沖左五分鐘就算<br />\n<br />\n食下生果吹下水搞呢搞路之後 3點半左右就訓<br />\n<br />\n亦係三晚最早訓嘅一晚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e1600ff1b11110eca4e908084928c8be77f68d6","tid":146251,"uid":33988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T09:59:22.000Z","msg":"《第二日》<br />\n<br />\n今日一早去睇鳴門漩渦 睇鳴門漩渦得潮漲潮退兩段時間有得睇 而當天就係9點半左右同黃昏5點左右<br />\n<br />\n睇漩渦有三間公司揀 睇自己需要啦<br />\n<br />\nうずしお汽船 -- 細船，可以超近漩渦，冇咁定<br />\n鳴門觀光汽船 -- 大船，多人，定，可以連埋渦之道買<br />\n漩渦觀潮船－咸臨丸 -- 淡路島上船，大，特色帆船<br />\n<br />\n我地係揀左最細最近果間うずしお汽船，搭9點半果班 去全家買左幾支嘢飲幾嚿飯團就揸去碼頭喇<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/175255_85238f6901033eadf6526decdab479d7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F175255_85238f6901033eadf6526decdab479d7.jpg&h=30af0d0f&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/175256_767d439051d3f62898d22a68eda15ed7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F175256_767d439051d3f62898d22a68eda15ed7.jpg&h=599e2d06&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/175257_ffa660caac9749f62502a2e957e1d47f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F175257_ffa660caac9749f62502a2e957e1d47f.jpg&h=56be98f1&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/175259_4dc6e6a07890307766193e880f26f8cc.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F175259_4dc6e6a07890307766193e880f26f8cc.jpg&h=f2fba1d5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n只能講太自然好神奇 亦一個非常值得來參觀嘅一個地方<br />\n<br />\n睇完上觀景台hae下抖下就出發神戶喇<br />\n亦係今次旅程重點環節<br />\n神戶勝利船<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"96627cc73c5da75c92ea855678b8e4eb26832973","tid":146251,"uid":45215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T10:00:23.000Z","msg":"留名"},{"pid":"2914f7b266d933f6cd11d86aabe42854efef6767","tid":146251,"uid":33988,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T14:05:41.000Z","msg":"《繼續第二日》<br />\n<br />\n睇完漩渦即刻揸上神戶 個零鐘車之後就到左第一個景點 新長田鐵人廿八公園<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/213113_fbf39cff70b62365a05e06991978767f.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F213113_fbf39cff70b62365a05e06991978767f.jpg&h=389be798&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n沿路會經過連接淡路同神戶嘅大橋同摩天輪<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3sP5V42.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3sP5V42.jpg&h=e04e4b7e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n第一次踏足本洲非常興奮<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/213308_ed47a312397e943e4610f714cd131d4c.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F213308_ed47a312397e943e4610f714cd131d4c.jpg&h=a1834564&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n喺新長田駅泊好車後 去到鐵人廿八公園 雖然唔係fans 但幾個麻甩佬見到咁大隻公仔都係好興奮<br />\n<br />\n食完飯之後出發去御畸公園睇神戶勝利船對新潟天鵝 話說本身plan神戶嘅時候只係因為想食神戶牛 但適逢見到原來果日有主場比賽 仲要係開季第一場主場 就plan埋落去喇 拿拿臨上網買波飛買泊車劵<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Xcc6Mhy.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FXcc6Mhy.jpg&h=5226cd53&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n球場氣氛相當好呀 出面有好多唔同嘅攤位 大家好有秩序咁排隊入去 果日第一場主場仲每位球迷都送打氣波衫一件 <br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/214132_8ed5ec2dd126c2bc36c4aa3ef754c294.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F214132_8ed5ec2dd126c2bc36c4aa3ef754c294.jpg&h=dc5d8811&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/214133_0933639d113687e1968d0f99a43e6575.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F214133_0933639d113687e1968d0f99a43e6575.jpg&h=fd6b35f4&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/214133_b696881028759cb96db09b0e6f3de5ea.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F214133_b696881028759cb96db09b0e6f3de5ea.jpg&h=23bf98aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有成三萬人入場差唔多爆滿 氣氛相當之高漲 太遲入場得番龍門後面坐 但個位相當靚 仲好近咁睇到兩個入波<br />\n<br />\n最後2:1贏左大家都好開心 致勝嘅第二球仲要係全場球迷出力打氣入波嘅 終於感受到主場優勢係咩<br />\n香港真係可以完全收皮<br />\n<br />\n睇完場波出番三宮食今晚嘅晚餐<br />\n<br />\n神戶牛<br />\n<br />\n上網搵到間又平又好食嘅餐廳 叫grilled missho <br />\n套餐有前菜 沙律 餐湯 石燒神戶牛 神戶牛漢堡扒 同咖哩飯 都係5500yen 抵撚到爛<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/64u9BKz.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F64u9BKz.jpg&h=d5bc7801&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/214648_58c57d1533fb368901bbc1145042639d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F214648_58c57d1533fb368901bbc1145042639d.jpg&h=536ee80a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n其他冇影相 神戶牛燒得好香 唔係好薄果種入口即溶 但都非常淋身好食 醬都無落加兩粒鹽已經好食到不得了 <br />\n<br />\n不過呢餐都係成個旅程排第二嘅一餐 最好食嘅反而喺之後嘅行程<br />\n<br />\n食完晚餐就揸埋去大阪 9個字車程<br />\n去大阪嘅原因係純粹想過去行下食下宵夜 因為大家都未去過同番淡路夜晚都冇嘢行冇嘢玩冇嘢食<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/54xT4r6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F54xT4r6.jpg&h=abc5d3ff&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/215633_62bd0bbc74d5032f6ceced697a429662.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F215633_62bd0bbc74d5032f6ceced697a429662.jpg&h=ae39d2d0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4thQ24.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4thQ24.jpg&h=30ebcfec&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/215635_b98ed881752db060d270d7aefe15da07.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F215635_b98ed881752db060d270d7aefe15da07.jpg&h=e7e3a6aa&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/114DBa4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F114DBa4.jpg&h=18e65d5b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/215714_939379758e656935235daa28ccc631eb.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F215714_939379758e656935235daa28ccc631eb.jpg&h=f8a25600&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/215716_09515e484ee113d143477c00e23fcdaa.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F215716_09515e484ee113d143477c00e23fcdaa.jpg&h=cb091439&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/215745_619691b4f32e3730bae9cbcd7ebf42ab.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F215745_619691b4f32e3730bae9cbcd7ebf42ab.jpg&h=256268d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/90535L2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F90535L2.jpg&h=1bd16365&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n好城市嘅大阪自然多人好多建築物高好多車多好多 亦喺呢個城市見到三種呢兩日都冇見過嘅人 <br />\n<br />\n雞 古惑仔同香港人<br />\n<br />\n行左陣就去磯丸食宵夜 唔知係咪超級旅遊區嘅關係 呢到嘅店員冇咁好禮貌 亦可能係咁啲野都冇咁好食<br />\n<br />\n食埋大阪王將之後就揸番淡路 佢個餃子真係好食 皮薄餡靚 外脆內軟<br />\n<br />\n揸番個幾兩個鐘車番到淡路涼都冇沖累到淨係刷左個牙就訓左<br />\n<br />\n訓覺果陣係4點半 即係呢一日足足玩左廿個中"},{"pid":"a909fa8bf059a17d4e7a493f556b482a995a9a62","tid":146251,"uid":128930,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-09T15:51:13.000Z","msg":"冇更新<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"}]}